=head1 DESCRIPTION

Consists of a Amazon Web Services Free Tier offerE<rsquo>s metadata and
your data usage for the offer.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActualUsageAmount => Num

Describes the actual usage accrued month-to-day (MTD) that you've used
so far.


=head2 Description => Str

The description of the Free Tier offer.


=head2 ForecastedUsageAmount => Num

Describes the forecasted usage by the month that you're expected to
use.


=head2 FreeTierType => Str

Describes the type of the Free Tier offer. For example, the offer can
be C<"12 Months Free">, C<"Always Free">, and C<"Free Trial">.


=head2 Limit => Num

Describes the maximum usage allowed in Free Tier.


=head2 Operation => Str

Describes C<usageType> more granularly with the specific Amazon Web
Service API operation. For example, this can be the C<RunInstances> API
operation for Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud.


=head2 Region => Str

Describes the Amazon Web Services Region for which this offer is
applicable


=head2 Service => Str

The name of the Amazon Web Service providing the Free Tier offer. For
example, this can be Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud.


=head2 Unit => Str

Describes the unit of the C<usageType>, such as C<Hrs>.


=head2 UsageType => Str

Describes the usage details of the offer. For example, this might be
